p: Table 2 indicates the various chemical constituents identified in PLEO. The yield of extraction was 0.42 ± 0.02% and it characterized by variety of components in less percentage. The main compounds present are terpinen-4-ol (11.49%), germacrene D (8.64%), α-Pinene (5.97%), sabinene (5.19%), caryophyllene (5.10%) and δ-Cadinene (4.86%).
